                <head>No. 981<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On November 13–14, President <persName corresp="#p_EISENHOWER1"
                        >Eisenhower</persName> made a State visit to Canada. Information concerning
                    preparations for the visit and a <pb facs="1023" n="2113" xml:id="pg_2113"/>
                    summary of the social events and official meetings that took place is <ref
                        target="#d982">
                        <hi rend="italic">infra</hi>
                    </ref>.</p>
            </div>
